ad-url=no}}</ref>西紐約閃電在例行賽取得排名第一的成績，並且在同年獲得總冠軍。<ref>{{cite web|title=Flash defeats Philly for the title|url=http://espn.go.com/espnw/news-opinion/6902464/wps-playoffs-western-new-york-flash-defeats-philadelphia-independence-title|date=August 27, 2011|publisher=ESPN|dead-url=yes|access-date=August 22, 2012|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111102134545/http://espn.go.com/espnw/news-opinion/6902464/wps-playoffs-western-new-york-flash-defeats-philadelphia-independence-title|archive-date=2011-11-02}}</ref>

